  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"y equals 3,600 left parenthesis a right parenthesis Superscript x\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3,600</mn><msup><mfenced><mi>a</mi></mfenced><mi>x</mi></msup></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The given equation, where <math alttext=\"a\"><mi>a</mi>\n</math> is a positive constant, gives the predicted number of bacteria, <math alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi>\n</math>, in a growth medium <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math> hours after the number of bacteria was initially measured. According to the equation, what was the predicted number of bacteria initially measured in the growth medium?</p>",
